entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You defeated a camp of desert swoopers just outside of Mos Eisley.
entries.journal_entry_description: There is a camp of desert swoopers just outside of Mos Eisley. Go defeat some of the swoopers.
entries.journal_entry_title: Thieves and Thugs and Hoodlums, Oh My!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Defeat some desert swoopers and teach them to leave the citizens of Mos Eisley alone.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Peawp R'dawc and bask in the success of your efforts.
